project_descr: Reintegration Assistance to Liberia DDRR Programme Residual Caseloads Beneficiaries

outputs.output_descr: The project 'Reintegration Assistance to Liberia DDRR Programme Residual Caseload Beneficiaries' is designed to provide reintegration support to up to 8,789 ex-combatants who have not received any assistance from the DDRR Programme .
